---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Process | LEGEND INDUSTRIES">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-200 pb-5">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Process</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">Typical engagement flow for bulk requirement handling.</p>
    </header>

    <ol class="space-y-5 text-slate-800">
      <li>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">1. Requirement</h2>
        <p class="mt-1">Buyer shares requirement context including quantity range, use case, branding needs, and delivery location.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">2. Discussion</h2>
        <p class="mt-1">Materials, customization approach, and feasible production options are discussed for alignment.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">3. Sample and approval</h2>
        <p class="mt-1">Sample or mock reference is reviewed and finalized before production progression.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">4. Production</h2>
        <p class="mt-1">Manufacturing and branding execution is carried out as per approved requirement scope.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">5. Delivery</h2>
        <p class="mt-1">Dispatch is scheduled per agreed requirement context and destination.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <p class="mt-8 text-slate-700">
      Timelines and pricing are context-based and finalized after requirement discussion and approval alignment.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-700">For enquiries, refer to the <a class="underline underline-offset-4" href="/contact">Contact</a> page.</p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
